### ==================== TRANSFORMERS ====================

### 4.1 Create Square Transformer (500VA)
# Uses: EiLamination #1, WindingSpec #1 (Pri), WindingSpec #2 (Sec), Accessory #1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transformers/square
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Biến áp cách ly 500VA (Standard)",
  "model3dUrl": "http://example.com/models/ba500.glb",
  "eiLaminationId": 1,
  "laminationWeightKg": 3.5,
  "windings": [
    {
      "windingSpecId": 1,
      "weightKg": 0.3
    },
    {
      "windingSpecId": 2,
      "weightKg": 0.5
    }
  ],
  "accessories": [
    {
      "accessoryId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "accessoryId": 2,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 4.2 Get Transformer Details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transformers/1
Accept: application/json
